subSubSection.paragraph:
Type locality:
De Geer ( 1773 ) did not know the species origin, stated as Mali , Mourdiah in
Eades and Otte ( 2009 )
.
Geographic zones: Shoreline, Tellian Atlas, High Plateaux, Northern Sahara, Central Sahara.
Bioclimatic zones: Humid, subhumid, semiarid, arid, saharian.
